    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me out? im working on a report for my office and need a quick summary of the economic impacts that these new federal environmental regs are gonna have on small-scale manufacturing businesses. mainly just need to know what the main concerns or changes are gonna be for them.",
